summary:
I am passionate about using technology to drive innovation and improve outcomes for customers and businesses around the world. Through my work, I have gained experience in analyzing data, creating predictive models, and designing business models to deliver high-quality solutions that meet the unique needs of each client and help them achieve their goals. Successfully working in leveraging emerging technologies to increase the efficiency and sustainability of agriculture practices.

Current projects:

Smart Farming Platform & App
Monetization Digital Agricultural products and services 
ArcGIS platform
Sustainability in Agriculture

Looking to connect with others in the agriculture and technology industries, share ideas, and explore new opportunities for collaboration and growth.
